node.text:
I am so proud to be part of @voicesofyouth with @unicef_uk for #WorldChildrensDay
 
Through the partnership I got the opportunity to speak with the incredibly inspiring 13 year-old, Areej in Yemen. Together we discussed the challenges faced by young people in her home country including access to education and the coronavirus pandemic. Areej’s message of hope and wish for a future where every child, everywhere, can fulfil their dreams and potential is inspirational. I am honoured to be able to share it on my platform.
 
To find out more about the situation in Yemen and how Unicef is working to support children like Areej visit the link in my stories

I’m reading a great little book called ‘The Lion Inside’ ... the story makes us take a little look at ourselves and teaches us we should always look for the courage we have, might be more than we think💡maybe we all have a lion inside 🦁

Every donation to Save the Children will help the children and families who’ve been hardest hit by the coronavirus crisis around the world. Please give what you can and stay safe x

Book by @rachelbrightbooks, illustrated by @_jimfield  published by @scholasticinc and @hachettebooks
@savechildrenuk

node.text: I can't wait for my new #HeresToTheFuture showcase next week, go check out the playlist and get to know these amazing artists. Oh, and happy #11YearsOfOneDirection!! ❤️

node.text: Today we lost a really great one in mr Tom O’Connor, I have a had the wonderful pleasure of getting to know you and your beautiful humor over the last few years and it brought me great joy to spend time with you. I have to thank you for the main gift you have given me in your son who has been there for me and mentored me through some of my most challenging days. You will be missed rest in peace

Tickets out now! Link in bio 🙌🏼

node.text: Father's Day is coming! I looked back with HUGO on all the things me and my Dad have done and it's safe to say I wouldn't be on this path without him 🙌🏼 #HappyFathersDay #HUGOMan #iamHUGO @hugo_official

THE ULTIMATE NFT EXPERIENCE TOKEN BROUGHT TO YOU BY FANCHAIN.
Dropping 15th June at 6:30pm BST /  1:30pm ET / 10:30am PT on @niftygateway.

Bringing the art to life, the auction winner and a guest will receive the exclusive invite to a once-in-a-lifetime immersive dining experience at Resorts World Las Vegas. This event will provide the opportunity to dine with the art creators Zedd, Sillygabe, Gary Vee and myself plus a selection of crypto leaders from around the world, including Nifty Gateway Founders Duncan and Griffin Cock Foster; crypto and psychedelics evangelist, Christian Angermayer; Galaxy Digital CEO, Mike Novogratz; Founder and CEO of Block.one. Brendan Blumer; Founder of Social Chain, Steven Bartlett; DJ/Producer and pioneer in the crypto/NFT space, 3LAU; innovative businesswoman and successful NFT creator Paris Hilton and other very special guests.

THE PHYSICAL TOKEN
The physical token also includes a bespoke commemorative presentation box containing the world’s leading holographic display, The Looking Glass Portrait with audio delivered by a JBL speaker. An authentication laminate signed by the creator’s and a custom made Lonely Bug commemorative coin. 
Plus: a unique QR code directing the owner to a special ‘Director’s Cut’ edit of the short digital film ‘Making Of Lonely Bug Collection’ which features unreleased footage from the day of the drop showing the creators' reactions when the winning bids came in.
#lonelybug

node.text:
This is the most exclusive thing i've ever been a part of!! There's six unique pieces of the #LonelyBug collection up for grabs next week created by myself, @zedd, @_sillygabe_ and featuring @garyvee. 
June 15th 6:30pm BST /  1:30pm ET / 10:30am PT on @niftygateway #SeeYouInVegas #ResortsWorld

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Liam Payne on June 11, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, beard and standing.

node.text:
Although I’ve been investing in and buying crypto for some years now I’m still keen to take you guys on this new journey of NFTs with me as I figure it out… In a few days, the 15th June, I’ll be launching my first ever NFT collection alongside @zedd and @_sillygabe_, and even featuring @garyvee on the rarest 1 of 1 piece!
This has been months and months of solid work for the team around the globe, so thank you for tuning in and being part of it 🙌🏼 So get ready… I’ve never attempted anything this crazy before #LonelyBug #SeeYouInVegas
